Query 14 — Lab availability by day of week
--student-name: Cao Quang Hung
--target-user: student
================================================================================

SQL logic review:
  ✓ DECLARE parameters: @space_types (VARCHAR), @lookback_year (INT)
  ✓ CTE lab_spaces: uses STRING_SPLIT(@space_types) for flexible filtering
  ✓ CTE total_labs: single-row count for availability computation
  ✓ CTE booked_days: finds distinct (dow_num, space_id) for occupied labs
  ✓ Main SELECT: 7-day VALUES grid, LEFT JOIN to booked_days, GROUP BY day
  ✓ Computes available_labs = total - COUNT(DISTINCT booked space_id) per day
  ✓ CASE status column: "All labs available" vs "Reduced availability"
  ✓ Respects is_deleted = 0 on bookings
  ✓ Uses explicit JOINs and normalized DOW formula
  ✓ Enum values match docs/tech-stack.md
  ✓ Only 3 CTEs and ~40 lines — much simpler than previous version

Expected output with default params (2 labs, 1-year lookback):
